"No Other Land" covers five years of recordings (2019-2023) at the home of Palestinian journalist Basel Adra> in the group of villages of Masafer Yatta, in the occupied West Bank, showing the demolitions of houses, schools, water wells and roads by the Israeli army and which continue today.
